msgid ""
"KHR Simple Controller [json](https://gitlab.kitware.com/vtk/vtk/-/blob/"
"master/Rendering/OpenXR/vtk_openxr_binding_khr_simple_controller.json)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/Rendering/OpenXR/README.md:27
